Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.32,台词,,0,0,0,,你说过 不会有下一次\N{\fs12}you said, "never again."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:25.24,台词,,0,0,0,,是的 -然后昨天晚上 突然间地\N{\fs12}Right. -And then last night out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.70,台词,,0,0,0,,你就扑向我\N{\fs12}you threw yourself at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.10,台词,,0,0,0,,哇 哇 哇偶 我扑向了你\N{\fs12}Wh-Wh-whoa. Threw myself at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.18,台词,,0,0,0,,是啊 -你说什么呢\N{\fs12}Yeah. -What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.38,台词,,0,0,0,,Hugh 我是喝得太多了 好吗\N{\fs12}Hugh, I had too much to drink, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.78,台词,,0,0,0,,酒后乱性了\N{\fs12}I made a bad decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.64,台词,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么人们常说说 不要喝太多酒 对吧\N{\fs12}That's why people say, don't have so much to drink, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.56,台词,,0,0,0,,所以我会不再喝多了\N{\fs12}So I won't drink so much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.56,台词,,0,0,0,,这种事不会再发生了 我们再也不用谈论它了\N{\fs12}This won't happen again, we never have to talk about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.28,台词,,0,0,0,,永远不要喝酒 不要酒后乱性 不要醉后谈论\N{\fs12}Never drink, never make a bad decision, never talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.36,台词,,0,0,0,,三大点\N{\fs12}The big three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.08,台词,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事 怎么了\N{\fs12}What happened? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.84,台词,,0,0,0,,你们太奇怪了\N{\fs12}You guys are being weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.64,台词,,0,0,0,,你生我的气吗 你为什么生我的气\N{\fs12}You're mad at me? Why are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.14,台词,,0,0,0,,你们总是迟到 我不需要你们来谴责我\N{\fs12}You guys are late all the time, I don't need the firing squad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.98,台词,,0,0,0,,因为我比平时晚一点\N{\fs12}because I'm a little later than normal, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.22,台词,,0,0,0,,好吧 我去了贝弗利山庄吃早餐\N{\fs12}Fine, I went to Beverly Hills for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.60,台词,,0,0,0,,这就是你们要答案\N{\fs12}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.48,台词,,0,0,0,,你为什么要去] 贝弗利山庄吃早餐\N{\fs12}Why would you go to Beverly Hills for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.74,台词,,0,0,0,,那里有很棒的餐厅 所以我\N{\fs12}They have great restaurants that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.61,台词,,0,0,0,,我在那里吃早饭啊\N{\fs12}and I eat breakfast there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.32,台词,,0,0,0,,你和谁吃的早饭\N{\fs12}Who'd you have breakfast with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.16,台词,,0,0,0,,和我自己\N{\fs12}It was just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.26,台词,,0,0,0,,为什么我们干嘛要谈论\N{\fs12}Why are we even talking about every thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.96,台词,,0,0,0,,这些我们生活中无聊的琐事\N{\fs12}that happens in each of our lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.06,台词,,0,0,0,,因为我们不需要  -你跟Ben谈过了吗\N{\fs12}'Cause we do not have to do that. -Have you talked to Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.15,台词,,0,0,0,,就今天早上 我和Ben吃早餐了\N{\fs12}Like, this morning. Did I have breakfast with Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.20,台词,,0,0,0,,等等 你是和Ben吃的早餐 -对呀\N{\fs12}Wait, you had breakfast with Ben? -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.64,台词,,0,0,0,,为了我们的电影 -我们都还没有提到过它\N{\fs12}About our movie? -We didn't even talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.44,台词,,0,0,0,,你是和Ben Falcone一起吃的早饭\N{\fs12}You had breakfast with Ben Falcone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.30,台词,,0,0,0,,然后你们都没有说起过我们的电影\N{\fs12}and you did not talk about our movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.87,台词,,0,0,0,,这是另一回事\N{\fs12}This was about a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.58,台词,,0,0,0,,什么另一件事\N{\fs12}What different thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.26,台词,,0,0,0,,跟你无关 那不是\N{\fs12}It doesn't involve you. This is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.24,台词,,0,0,0,,我们不需要\N{\fs12}We don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.61,台词,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fs12}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.45,台词,,0,0,0,,淡定 好吗 谢谢你了\N{\fs12}Back off, all right? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.24,台词,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.42,台词,,0,0,0,,我需要吃点东西 行吗\N{\fs12}I need to eat something. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.62,台词,,0,0,0,,我和Ben早饭的时候什么都没吃\N{\fs12}I didn't eat anything at my breakfast with Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:52.64,台词,,0,0,0,,那的东西都好贵啊\N{\fs12}Everything was so expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.16,台词,,0,0,0,,我都不知道谁要买单\N{\fs12}I didn't know who was gonna pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.39,台词,,0,0,0,,打死也不去贝弗利山庄吃早饭了\N{\fs12}Never eat breakfast in Beverly Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.93,台词,,0,0,0,,你和Ben见面干嘛\N{\fs12}What were you meeting Ben for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.46,台词,,0,0,0,,为了我的真人秀\N{\fs12}My reality show idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.30,台词,,0,0,0,,喜剧小品版的《美国偶像》吗\N{\fs12}That "American Idol" sketch comedy thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.45,台词,,0,0,0,,赢的人可以上《周六夜现场》\N{\fs12}where the winner goes on "Saturday Night Live,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.55,台词,,0,0,0,,这永远不会发生\N{\fs12}a thing that can never happen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.99,台词,,0,0,0,,因为你没有合法的联系\N{\fs12}because you have no legal connection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.02,台词,,0,0,0,,不管是《周六夜现场》还是《美国偶像》\N{\fs12}to either "Saturday Night Live" or "American Idol."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.61,台词,,0,0,0,,是的 我很清楚\N{\fs12}Yes, I'm very aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.55,台词,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我想要找个名人\N{\fs12}That's why I'm trying to get a celebrity attached
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.88,台词,,0,0,0,,来推销它\N{\fs12}to try to help sell it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.01,台词,,0,0,0,,所以我问Ben 他是否会让Melissa参与进来\N{\fs12}so I asked Ben if he'd get Melissa involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.38,台词,,0,0,0,,我的天 -什么鬼\N{\fs12}Oh, my God! -What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.45,台词,,0,0,0,,什么什么鬼\N{\fs12}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.49,台词,,0,0,0,,Larry 我们需要请Ben和Melissa来演《第一男夫人》\N{\fs12}Larry, we need Ben and Melissa for "Mr. First Lady,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:26.06,台词,,0,0,0,,而不是你那和我们无关的愚蠢真人秀\N{\fs12}not your stupid reality show that we're not even a part of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.93,台词,,0,0,0,,那就是你生气的原因吗\N{\fs12}Is that why you're mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.19,台词,,0,0,0,,就因为没搭上你们一起\N{\fs12}Because you're not involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.41,台词,,0,0,0,,我们是结婚了吗 就不能\N{\fs12}What are we, married and not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.50,台词,,0,0,0,,被允许做自己的事吗\N{\fs12}to do anything on our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.13,台词,,0,0,0,,这是一个邪教吗\N{\fs12}This is a cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.67,台词,,0,0,0,,你能把太阳镜拿掉吗\N{\fs12}Could you take those sunglasses off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:39.91,台词,,0,0,0,,当然可以 只要你们别那么烦躁\N{\fs12}Sure. As soon as you guys take your bad moods off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.34,台词,,0,0,0,,开心了吧\N{\fs12}Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.75,台词,,0,0,0,,这不是我的球\N{\fs12}This is not my ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.65,台词,,0,0,0,,是Hugh的蠢球 -我才不想要那个该死的球\N{\fs12}It's Hugh's stupid ball! -I don't want the damn ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.75,台词,,0,0,0,,噢 -哇\N{\fs12}Whoa! -Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.92,台词,,0,0,0,,早上好 大家\N{\fs12}Morning, team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.59,台词,,0,0,0,,卧槽 什么鬼 什么时候搞的\N{\fs12}Holy crackers, when did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.02,台词,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.26,台词,,0,0,0,,一定是一只鸟或者\N{\fs12}That must have been a bird or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.20,台词,,0,0,0,,可怜的小家伙\N{\fs12}Poor little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.69,台词,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就是想来个突袭 看看事情进展的怎么样\N{\fs12}Well, just wanted to pop in, see how things are going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.88,台词,,0,0,0,,看看写到哪了\N{\fs12}see how the writing's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.01,台词,,0,0,0,,呃 快完成了\N{\fs12}Uh... we're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.11,台词,,0,0,0,,很好 很好 Connie会很开心的\N{\fs12}Good, good. Connie will like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.81,台词,,0,0,0,,在这世上我最喜欢的事就是\N{\fs12}And I know my favorite thing in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.88,台词,,0,0,0,,坐在那 手里拿着一袋奇多\N{\fs12}is sitting back with a bag of Cheetos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.78,台词,,0,0,0,,读一本刚出炉的《放屁人》剧本\N{\fs12}reading a fresh "Fartlemans" script.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.51,台词,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.92,台词,,0,0,0,,嘿Tamara\N{\fs12}Hey, Tamara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:27.42,台词,,0,0,0,,你能不能打个电话 问问窗户的报价\N{\fs12}Can you call around and get some quotes on some windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.22,台词,,0,0,0,,呃 事实上 我们才写了4页\N{\fs12}Uh, actually, we're on page four,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.79,台词,,0,0,0,,还早着呢 你个白痴\N{\fs12}so not almost done, you psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.59,台词,,0,0,0,,我又不知道他会这样说\N{\fs12}I didn't know that was gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.60,台词,,0,0,0,,好吧 你知道吗 木已成舟\N{\fs12}All right, you know what? What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:41.67,台词,,0,0,0,,所以 有人告诉Ben了吗 他有读过我们的剧本了吗\N{\fs12}So... has anyone talked to Ben? Has he read our script?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.94,台词,,0,0,0,,你现在是认真的吗\N{\fs12}Are you serious right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.80,台词,,0,0,0,,吃早饭的时候你怎么不问他\N{\fs12}Why didn't you ask him at breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.04,台词,,0,0,0,,反而谈你愚蠢的附带项目\N{\fs12}instead of talking about your dumb side project?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.27,台词,,0,0,0,,我们又没结婚\N{\fs12}We're not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.94,台词,,0,0,0,,我们可以做其他的事情\N{\fs12}We're allowed to do other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.51,台词,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Uhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.98,台词,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs12}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.55,台词,,0,0,0,,我要在我车里吃午饭\N{\fs12}I'm gonna eat my lunch in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.91,台词,,0,0,0,,那你不是好棒棒\N{\fs12}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.25,台词,,0,0,0,,简直有毒\N{\fs12}Well, this is toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:06.15,台词,,0,0,0,,你真的不打算告诉我们咱要在这里做什么吗\N{\fs12}Are you seriously not gonna tell us what we're doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:06.93,台词,,0,0,0,,我已经告诉过你们\N{\fs12}I already told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.00,台词,,0,0,0,,当你们需要知道的时候我会说的\N{\fs12}I'll tell you when you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.54,台词,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Um... tch-tch-tch-tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.21,台词,,0,0,0,,美容牙科\N{\fs12}Cosmetic dentistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.34,台词,,0,0,0,,你觉得我需要镶牙\N{\fs12}You think I need veneers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.83,台词,,0,0,0,,因为我牙缝大\N{\fs12}'cause I have giant gaps in my teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.75,台词,,0,0,0,,嗯 镶个牙又不会怎么了\N{\fs12}Well, veneers wouldn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.08,台词,,0,0,0,,呃 哦 呃 402\N{\fs12}Uh, oh, uh, 402.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.88,台词,,0,0,0,,治疗和咨询\N{\fs12}Therapy and counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.63,台词,,0,0,0,,讲真 你要带我们去看心理治疗师\N{\fs12}Seriously, you're taking us to a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.46,台词,,0,0,0,,我才不要看心理治疗师 疯了吧\N{\fs12}I'm not gonna see a therapist. This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.55,台词,,0,0,0,,我不觉得这事有什么\N{\fs12}I don't think it's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.06,台词,,0,0,0,,我是说 运动团队也去看心理治疗师而我们就是个团队\N{\fs12}I mean, sports teams see therapists and we're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.69,台词,,0,0,0,,我们是个有一堆大问题的团队\N{\fs12}We're a team that has massive problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.76,台词,,0,0,0,,不是一堆问题 是一个问题 你就是那个问题\N{\fs12}Not problems, problem. You are the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.77,台词,,0,0,0,,真正的问题是 Ben Falcone得花多久才能读完剧本\N{\fs12}The real problem is how long does it take Ben Falcone to read a script?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:42.17,台词,,0,0,0,,说真的 他是不是不识字啊 我很认真地在问这个问题哦\N{\fs12}I mean, is he illiterate? I'm seriously asking that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.39,台词,,0,0,0,,真是简直了 我是说 他也没回我呢\N{\fs12}It's absolutely crazy. I mean, he hasn't gotten back to me about my thing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.91,台词,,0,0,0,,我的天 你开玩笑吗\N{\fs12}Oh, my God. Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.02,台词,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我很高兴我们在这看心理治疗师\N{\fs12}You know what? I'm glad we're here seeing a therapist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.56,台词,,0,0,0,,因为我需要有人跟我解释\N{\fs12}'cause I need someone to explain to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.01,台词,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么疯\N{\fs12}why you are so insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.28,台词,,0,0,0,,火气真大\N{\fs12}So much anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.45,台词,,0,0,0,,治疗费用记在你保险上 对吧\N{\fs12}This is going on your insurance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.15,台词,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么鬼\N{\fs12}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.69,台词,,0,0,0,,哦 得了吧 你从来没见过那个吗\N{\fs12}Oh, come on. You've never seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.36,台词,,0,0,0,,你按个按钮 他办公室里的提示灯就亮了\N{\fs12}You press the button, a light goes on in his office
