Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.46,台词,,0,0,0,,然后敲出另一份《放屁人》剧本 我们可处于顺风顺水的时候\N{\fs12}and knocking out another "Fartlemans" script? We're on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.37,台词,,0,0,0,,或是我们可以顺着走廊走 找到Connie再杀掉她 我都做好准备了\N{\fs12}That or we can go down the hall and murder Connie. I'm up for either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:16.14,台词,,0,0,0,,我会的 但是我绝对会感到不舒服的\N{\fs12}I would, but I am definitely getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.95,台词,,0,0,0,,而我有Lois 然后我的保姆有一些事我要去处理\N{\fs12}And I have Lois and my nanny has something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.21,台词,,0,0,0,,但我们可以明天再做\N{\fs12}but we'll do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.95,台词,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我会做好自己那份的\N{\fs12}You know what? I'll do one on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.32,台词,,0,0,0,,-真的吗  -是啊\N{\fs12}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:26.09,台词,,0,0,0,,不 不 我们什么都在一起写\N{\fs12}No, no, we write everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.72,台词,,0,0,0,,啊哦 走\N{\fs12}Uh-uh, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.86,台词,,0,0,0,,-你们有自己的生活和家庭 -我来吧\N{\fs12}- You guys have got lives and families - I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.97,台词,,0,0,0,,行 嗯 工作别太拼\N{\fs12}Okay, well, don't work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:37.26,台词,,0,0,0,,但足够认真到可以做我们所有的工作就好\N{\fs12}But work hard enough where you do all our work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.23,台词,,0,0,0,,没问题 Lar\N{\fs12}You got it, Lar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.77,台词,,0,0,0,,Hugh\N{\fs12}Hugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.06,台词,,0,0,0,,我只想谢谢你什么都没说出去\N{\fs12}I just want to thank you for not saying anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.37,台词,,0,0,0,,你知道 当我们在\N{\fs12}you know, when we were at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.38,台词,,0,0,0,,Blaine Kaine的办公室\N{\fs12}Blaine Kaine's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:52.98,台词,,0,0,0,,受尊敬的非医生Blaine Kaine\N{\fs12}The esteemed non-doctor Blaine Kaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.95,台词,,0,0,0,,只是我们一起工作而我有个孩子\N{\fs12}It's just we work together and I have a kid and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.89,台词,,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\fs12}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.15,台词,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:03.29,台词,,0,0,0,,我是说 你有你的顾虑\N{\fs12}I mean, you have your concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.99,台词,,0,0,0,,我没有任何这些顾虑 但\N{\fs12}I have none of those concerns, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.83,台词,,0,0,0,,我尊重你的顾虑\N{\fs12}I respect your concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.30,台词,,0,0,0,,所以我们没问题吧\N{\fs12}So we're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.70,台词,,0,0,0,,是 我们没有问题\N{\fs12}Yes, we're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.04,台词,,0,0,0,,我是说 我们身处一段多方关系\N{\fs12}I mean, we're in a polyamorous relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.57,台词,,0,0,0,,跟Larry Dorf 无性关系\N{\fs12}nonsexual, with Larry Dorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.78,台词,,0,0,0,,那是我从小一直的梦想\N{\fs12}That was always my dream growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.41,台词,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.18,台词,,0,0,0,,-你在干什么 -我在试着使眼色\N{\fs12}- What are you doing?- I'm trying to wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.12,台词,,0,0,0,,那叫使眼色吗\N{\fs12}That's winking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.82,台词,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么使眼色\N{\fs12}I don't know how to wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.15,台词,,0,0,0,,呃 好吧\N{\fs12}Uh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.79,台词,,0,0,0,,好 明天见\N{\fs12}All right, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.12,台词,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}All right.
